
mp4creator <options> mp4-file 
	-t 				// list track information
	-c <track-file> // create track from file
	-ch <track-file> // create track and hint track from file
	-h <track-id>	// hint trackId
	-i				// interleave mdat's
	-hi				// hint interleave (audio tracks only)
	-p <payload-name>	// choose RTP payload format
	-d <track-id>	// delete trackid and any associated hint tracks
					// TBD delete associated data
	-s				// make streamable, i.e. moov first, mdat's last
					// implies -i ?

mp4encode becomes:
	mp4creator -ch foo.divx foo.mp4
	mp4creator -ch -p 3119 foo.mp3 foo.mp4

Phlilips exercise becomes:
	mp4creator -t phlips.mp4
	mp4creator -h 3 philips.mp4
	mp4creator -h 4 philips.mp4

mp4-file created if DNE, else opened rw
od & bifs tracks are automatic

Creatable/Hintable types
.mp3
	RFC 2250 | RFC 3119
.aac
	ISMA
.divx | .mp4v
	RFC 3016

Per type
	virtual GetConfiguration
		list of name value pairs
	virtual GetSample

list track info
	MP4Read()
create and create and hint
	MP4Create() or MP4Clone() depending on if file already exists
hint
	MP4Clone()
delete track
	MP4Clone()
streamable
	MP4Clone()?
